sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Premium User
    participant FE as React<br/>CustomVisualizationPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>AlertAnalyticsView
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Select metrics, chart type, time range
    FE->>API: GET /api/analytics/?metric=severity&chart=bar&range=7d
    API->>DB: Alert.objects.filter(timestamp__gte=start).values("severity").annotate(Count)
    DB-->>API: Aggregated analytics data
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {labels: [...], datasets: [...]}
    FE->>FE: Render Recharts component (Bar / Line / Pie)
    FE-->>U: Display custom visualization chart
